**Town Elder** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous | Haunted
__Basics__
The Town Elder will survive the first night attack against them, but is banished upon a second attack.
__Details__
The Town Elder is not informed if they survive an attack.
If the Town Elder is killed in any way after surving a night attack, they are immediately banished.
If the Town Elder dies *before* using their defense (i.e. lynching or day kill), they will become a ghost as normal.

__Simplified__
The Town Elder will survive the first night attack against them, but will be immediately banished upon a second attack.

__Formalized__
Starting: Protect @Self from `Attacks` through Partial Defense during Night (~UntilUse)
On Death: True Banish @Self

__Card__
The Town Elder can survive one attack before dying of old age.
